{"tid":1159833,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【TG】絲打球迷谷","createTime":"2019-05-18T04:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T15:57:01.000Z","uid":34567,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8dc92e0d3b1f91c3e375eb45f00440fdedd87b","tid":1159833,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"【TG】絲打球迷谷<br />\n<br />\n話說知道唔少絲打都有睇波，於是開左個TG gp，聚集一班鍾意睇足球嘅絲打，一齊討論下足球同愛隊。本谷開咗一段時間，唔同球迷都有，氣氛和睦，歡迎足球bb同資深球迷加入。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家花少少時間答幾條非常簡單既問題，唔該晒～<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 記得PM 錄音俾我呀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/KNz3jqBPUbxAtM9f8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKNz3jqBPUbxAtM9f8&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e4f5671c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KNz3jqBPUbxAtM9f8</a>"},{"pid":"321242b6deb901f0808e78f212c43da0b9bbecca","tid":1159833,"uid":109853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"259da9c3ba9e4dae7f46aa6ba26e74e74f099d9f","tid":1159833,"uid":219466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a6bb806cfb40e63c64cfa618d8c7471b79c8d3f","tid":1159833,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32f06342f22e2d7f8ac9939b39290d93d0b8c490","tid":1159833,"uid":156522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"死狗公扮乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86a5c2e06ffbb2ab48c1afd0e9b4f8e627d3250","tid":1159833,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da7ad9c13ea8f3755830c4edd27dd2fde0bac3b2","tid":1159833,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32f06342f22e2d7f8ac9939b39290d93d0b8c490","tid":1159833,"uid":156522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"